{"id": "1263663256778838046", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　博學多聞的喚醒體不在少數，瑟菈就是其中之一。她對於那些禁忌的典籍尤為熟悉，經常指引調查員去大陸與大洋中的旮旯之處尋找遠古失落的秘密史書與魔法書。\n　　唯一的代價就是，她必須是第一個讀完這些書籍的人。圖書館中所有的資料經過她的重新編纂整理，更加易於閱讀與收藏。但校方並未因此將全部庫藏都交給她處理，因為她的文字底下總是藏著對某個偉大存在的感恩與崇拜。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://www.pinterest.com/pin/24910604184170564/)\n命輪圖示：[資料](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/array_4799910?term=fragment&page=1&position=6&origin=tag&related_id=4799910)、[額頭](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/array_4799910?term=fragment&page=1&position=6&origin=tag&related_id=4799910)", "timestamp": "2024-07-19T01:06:38.144000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1263663256866914315", "filename": "783a33589523d1ac.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 20063, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263663256866914315/783a33589523d1ac.jpg?ex=69cbc6de&is=69ca755e&hm=ffbacad266c248fadff250abe2b0a217cfa5ad2237c28ebdc4bdd3de2482b91e&"}, {"id": "1263663257105862666", "filename": "16b0a88bb0d4e2af.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 169173, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263663257105862666/16b0a88bb0d4e2af.jpg?ex=69cbc6de&is=69ca755e&hm=8e4cdde94164d8f9a6bc70a09953c70d0d01b391279923647f763056dd76620e&"}, {"id": "1263663257391206471", "filename": "3900db0c30d32b40.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 128985, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263663257391206471/3900db0c30d32b40.jpg?ex=69cbc6de&is=69ca755e&hm=ef84f4fcec63609e96e9cd78b3af8101074758477dca1301f50ea20c70fae1c8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
